lass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T15:55:18.000Z","msg":"星期日咁夜都要開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T15:59:56.000Z","msg":"一定係未睇過羽毛球比賽啦<br />\n咁叫-6?<br />\n唔好出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c67f1f9041126aec0bc87cbe2cf1ce8a30c9e18","tid":794741,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T16:00:39.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a594afbb2d80fdda79f8de861d2eb30ea82604c","tid":794741,"uid":9030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T16:44:40.000Z","msg":"在尾段港隊更表現出贏波決心和氣勢，在2次『刁時』後，鄧俊文最後以一球殺波完成賽事，二人即時雙手高舉，跪地慶祝！25日為港隊混雙歷史性奪牌後，鄧俊文和謝影雪再創歷史，『阿雪』坦言贏波因為心態調教得好：『因為上次南京太慘痛，被對手屠殺，所以今次贏波決心好強烈，但都係要諗自己係去衝佢哋，一定要相信自己可以發揮得好。』<br />\n<br />\n在第2局鄧俊文更曾經發生「蝦碌」事件，曾經有一球他以為已經得分，自己一個轉身慶祝，剩下謝影雪一人在場上奮戰，場面搞笑。雖然有失誤，但他對今場表現十分滿意：「其實無諗過可以入決賽，開頭目標係4強，入到決賽已經係意外收穫。」今天晚上二人將會再決賽再硬撼另一中國組合鄭思維、黃雅瓊，雙方5次交手「左手配」只有1勝，但總教練何一鳴對二人信心十足：「過咗4強，決賽就好有信心，因為佢哋係無壓力去打。」"},{"pid":"fc3f6d18ebff9fd8e878af17e2d8c6965e31239a","tid":794741,"uid":9030,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T16:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180826/photo/bkn-20180826222719200-0826_00882_001_04b.jpg?20180826231850\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180826%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180826222719200-0826_00882_001_04b.jpg%3F20180826231850&h=5b452ed6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df730c6d0904f94b7a39b885585a5cded8e833c4","tid":794741,"uid":7435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"謝映雪支拍真係好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95bf27be5365b412f1c70c85ef011b7665c7a6bd","tid":794741,"uid":2883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T17:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一片段"},{"pid":"bcc5dedfe913d67839ee273870ab5f21672574e0","tid":794741,"uid":2883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T17:32:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇片段</blockquote>"},{"pid":"42ee08e449695c596471de4504743bd7f0511dba","tid":794741,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df730c6d0904f94b7a39b885585a5cded8e833c4","tid":794741,"uid":7435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"謝映雪支拍真係好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T17:48:02.000Z","msg":"係咪自己畫架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\